Package: scpcR
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Correlation-Robust Inference for Regression Coefficients
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Boll", email = "david.boll@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Daniel", "Goettlich", email = "daniel.goettlich@econ.uzh.ch", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Implements spatial correlation-robust procedures for
    inference on regression coefficients using the SCPC approach of
    Mueller and Watson (2022) <doi:10.3982/ECTA19465> and Mueller and
    Watson (2023) <doi:10.1080/07350015.2022.2127737>.
